      cues:['Low-trauma vertebral fracture on long-term oral steroids \u2014 glucocorticoid-induced osteoporosis; a fragility fracture is diagnostic of osteoporosis.','START bone protection now (bisphosphonate + calcium/vitamin D), often WITHOUT waiting for DEXA given the fragility fracture/steroid; review/taper the steroid (steroid-sparing).','Honest, candour-style acknowledgement that steroids contributed and protection is needed \u2014 without blame; falls/lifestyle; consider myeloma/mets if atypical.']
